snippet.title: One Night at Flumpty's Trailer
snippet.description:
Reupload!  The trailer doesn't really apply anymore since the game's been out a long time, and it could be snazzier than it is, so I didn't want to upload it unless I had the trailer for ONAF2 to go along with it.  I'm glad someone had the ONAF2 trailer on hand!

Game here: https://gamejolt.com/games/onaf/124881
